caption.p: Four sub-models from the best model. The symbols “−” and “√” mean the absence and presence of interactions, respectively. Model 6 (i) no interactions between HMPV and RSV ( ϕ HMPV = ϕ RSV = 0); Model 6 (ii) influence of HMPV on RSV ( ϕ RSV ≠ 0, ϕ HMPV = 0), Model 6 (iii) influence of RSV on HMPV ( ϕ RSV = 0, ϕ HMPV ≠ 0) and Model 6 (iv) interactions between HMPV and RSV ( ϕ HMPV ≠ ϕ RSV ≠ 0)
